</it> and <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../221/479221.xml">
All Saints</link></series>
</it> make the journey west for the weekend to entertain the audience, visit sick children and read donations on air. In addition, musical guests are also a big part of the weekend. Over the years many acts including <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../263/52263.xml">
